{% extends "layouts/base.twig" %}

{% block title %}Prompt موقع مش شكله AI — اتعلم ببساطة{% endblock %}

{% block body_class %}learnsimply-tool-page-body{% endblock %}

{% block styles %}
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ theme_uri }}/assets/toolbox/tool-page.css" />
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<section class="ls-tool">
    <div class="ls-tool-container">

        {# ===== Back Link ===== #}
        <a href="/toolbox/" class="ls-tool-back">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
            صندوق الأدوات
        </a>

        {# ===== Header ===== #}
        <div class="ls-tool-header">
            <span class="ls-tool-badge">أداة مجانية</span>
            <h1 class="ls-tool-title">Prompt موقع مش شكله AI</h1>
            <p class="ls-tool-subtitle">أمر بتديه لأي AI (زي ChatGPT أو Claude) <strong>قبل</strong> ما تطلب منه يعملك موقع — عشان التصميم يطلع مختلف ومايبقاش الشكل المكرر اللي كل الناس بتاخده.</p>
        </div>

        {# ===== Terminal Code Block ===== #}
        <div class="ls-tool-terminal">
            <div class="ls-tool-terminal-bar">
                <span class="ls-tool-terminal-filename">design-prompt.txt</span>
                <div class="ls-tool-terminal-dots">
                    <span class="ls-tool-terminal-dot ls-tool-terminal-dot--red"></span>
                    <span class="ls-tool-terminal-dot ls-tool-terminal-dot--yellow"></span>
                    <span class="ls-tool-terminal-dot ls-tool-terminal-dot--green"></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ls-tool-terminal-body">
                <pre id="ls-tool-prompt-text">Use the following design philosophy for this project:

&lt;frontend_aesthetics&gt;
Before writing any code, define a bold aesthetic direction by answering:
1. What problem does this interface solve, and for whom?
2. What tone defines it? Choose one and fully commit: brutally minimal, maximalist, retro-futuristic, editorial, brutalist, art deco, organic, luxury, or playful.
3. What is the one thing users will remember most about this design?

Then implement the interface with strong visual intention. Match implementation complexity to the vision: maximalist design should include elaborate animations and layered effects, while refined minimalism should rely on precise spacing, typography, and subtle detail.

Design rules:
- Typography: Use distinctive, characterful fonts. Pair a unique display font with a refined body font. Avoid Inter, Roboto, Arial, Space Grotesk, and generic system fonts.
- Color &amp; Theme: Commit to one dominant palette with sharp accents. Use CSS variables for consistency. Avoid safe, evenly distributed palettes. Take inspiration from IDE themes and cultural aesthetics.
- Motion: Focus on memorable, high-impact motion. A strong page-load reveal with staggered animations is better than many weak hover effects. Use CSS-only motion for HTML and Motion library for React.
- Spatial Composition: Break rigid layouts. Use asymmetry, overlap, diagonal flow, generous negative space, or controlled density. Avoid default centered stacks.
- Backgrounds &amp; Texture: Add atmosphere using gradient meshes, noise, geometric patterns, layered transparency, grain, dramatic shadows, and decorative borders. Do not default to flat solid backgrounds unless the chosen aesthetic requires it.

Never use:
- Overused fonts like Inter, Roboto, Arial, Space Grotesk, or system defaults
- Generic color schemes, especially purple gradients on white
- Predictable centered layouts, standard card grids, or reusable-looking patterns
- Cookie-cutter design with no context-specific identity

Make bold, unexpected choices that feel tailored to this exact project. The final result should feel unique, memorable, and impossible to confuse with a generic template.
&lt;/frontend_aesthetics&gt;</pre>
            </div>
            <div class="ls-tool-copy-wrap">
                <button type="button" class="ls-tool-copy-btn" id="ls-tool-copy-btn">
                    <svg class="ls-tool-copy-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="9" y="9" width="13" height="13" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M5 15H4a2 2 0 01-2-2V4a2 2 0 012-2h9a2 2 0 012 2v1"/></svg>
                    <span class="ls-tool-copy-label">نسخ الأمر</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        {# ===== Steps ===== #}
        <div class="ls-tool-steps-section">
            <h2 class="ls-tool-steps-title">إزاي تستخدمه؟</h2>
            <div class="ls-tool-steps">
                <div class="ls-tool-step">
                    <div class="ls-tool-step-num">1</div>
                    <div class="ls-tool-step-content">
                        <div class="ls-tool-step-label">انسخ الأمر</div>
                        <div class="ls-tool-step-desc">اضغط على زرار "نسخ الأمر" فوق.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="ls-tool-step">
                    <div class="ls-tool-step-num">2</div>
                    <div class="ls-tool-step-content">
                        <div class="ls-tool-step-label">افتح أي AI</div>
                        <div class="ls-tool-step-desc">روح على <a href="https://chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ChatGPT</a> أو <a href="https://claude.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Claude</a> أو أي أداة بتستخدمها.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="ls-tool-step">
                    <div class="ls-tool-step-num">3</div>
                    <div class="ls-tool-step-content">
                        <div class="ls-tool-step-label">ابعت الأمر الأول</div>
                        <div class="ls-tool-step-desc">الصق الأمر اللي نسخته وابعته لوحده — ده بيحدد أسلوب التصميم.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="ls-tool-step">
                    <div class="ls-tool-step-num">4</div>
                    <div class="ls-tool-step-content">
                        <div class="ls-tool-step-label">اطلب الموقع</div>
                        <div class="ls-tool-step-desc">دلوقتي اطلب منه يعملك الموقع اللي أنت عايزه — هيطلع بتصميم مختلف تمامًا.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>
{% endblock %}

{% block scripts %}
<script>
(function(){
    var btn = document.getElementById('ls-tool-copy-btn');
    if(!btn) return;
    btn.addEventListener('click', function(){
        var pre = document.getElementById('ls-tool-prompt-text');
        if(!pre) return;
        var tmp = document.createElement('textarea');
        tmp.innerHTML = pre.innerHTML;
        var text = tmp.value;
        function done(){
            btn.classList.add('ls-tool-copy-btn--done');
            btn.querySelector('.ls-tool-copy-label').textContent = 'تم النسخ ✓';
            btn.querySelector('.ls-tool-copy-icon').style.display = 'none';
            setTimeout(function(){
                btn.classList.remove('ls-tool-copy-btn--done');
                btn.querySelector('.ls-tool-copy-label').textContent = 'نسخ الأمر';
                btn.querySelector('.ls-tool-copy-icon').style.display = '';
            }, 2200);
        }
        if(navigator.clipboard && window.isSecureContext){
            navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(done).catch(fb);
        } else { fb(); }
        function fb(){
            var ta = document.createElement('textarea');
            ta.value = text;
            ta.style.cssText = 'position:fixed;left:-9999px;top:-9999px;opacity:0';
            document.body.appendChild(ta);
            ta.focus(); ta.select();
            try{ document.execCommand('copy'); done(); }catch(e){}
            document.body.removeChild(ta);
        }
    });
})();
</script>
{% endblock %}
